works.description: At the ICFF 2011 in New York City, Mark Goetz and Efe Buluc presented their first production piece, which is a unique lounge chair that looks to be the toughest of all we have seen to date. Dubbed the Bulldozer Lounge, the industrially crafted chair enjoys a Transformers-like color scheme and appears to be designed to the extreme. The solid aluminum frame comes padded with foam/neoprene material and despite the sturdy looks, the chair is quite comfortable to lounge on.
